function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	idTownieClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(npc_Townie)
	idMeridanClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(npc_Meridan)
	idHunterAClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(npc_HunterA)
	idHunterBClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(npc_HunterB)
	
	-- Move townie out of the area and delete
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idTownieClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idTownieClone, marker_Townie_WalkTo, "npc_walk", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idTownieClone)
	end
	
	-- Moved Meridan to quest location and swap for static
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idMeridanClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idMeridanClone, marker_Meridan_WalkTo, "npc_walk", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idMeridanClone)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idHunterAClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idHunterAClone, marker_HunterA_WalkTo, "npc_walk", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idHunterAClone)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idHunterBClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idHunterBClone, marker_HunterB_WalkTo, "npc_walk", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idHunterBClone)
	end
end
